The segmentation by propulsion type highlights the dominance of the electric segment in the market's future landscape. Electric vehicles offer a plethora of advantages over traditional petrol or hybrid models, such as lower operational costs, reduced maintenance requirements, and a seamless riding experience. With a growing focus on sustainability and environmental consciousness, consumers are gravitating towards electric propulsion as a responsible and sustainable choice for their commuting needs. The electric segment is expected to witness significant growth in the coming years, driven by advancements in battery technology and an increasing emphasis on eco-friendly transportation solutions.

